{"tid":922172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國日常】河南狗販為多賺數十元 用水管給狗插胃灌水","createTime":"2018-11-30T07:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T01:06:39.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f411275b5ec0a3c2e72ce3a37026f1aa2732e3b4","tid":922172,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181130/_2018113011324714620.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181130%2F_2018113011324714620.jpg&h=1629a0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上周五（23日）內地有傳媒揭發河南偃師高龍鎮207國道邊的小樹林裏，有20多名狗販在給狗灌水。他們用鐵鉗卡頭、水管插胃，狗被灌水時絕望流淚，但還搖著尾巴。狗販稱，買來10元一斤，賣也是10元一斤，給狗灌兩三斤水，能多掙二、三十元，賺的都是給狗灌的水錢。<br />\n<br />\n狗販又表示：「抓著灌灌水，兩隻狗能掙六十多塊錢。有人已經這麼幹了十幾年。」<br />\n<br />\n可見此類殘忍的事件並非首個案例，事件曝光後引發網民極大的憤慨，有網民憤怒地表示：「生而為人 請你們善良！」、「我開始相信有十八層地獄了！」、「前兩天是牛，現在是狗，這些人的良心呢？」、「吃肉是本能，尊重是人性，虐殺動物就為了那麼點錢的顯然沒有人性。」、「看見動物嗷嗷叫的哭求，心裡真的不會痛麼？」、「六十塊錢。有手有腳，幹點甚麼不能掙來六十塊。」、「可以不愛，但請不要傷害！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/876865\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F876865&d=XJlrGENh4tChnQbLgu56%2FU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=835d340a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F876865&h=f6bff575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/876865</a><br />\n<br />\n上一單<br />\n[強國日常] 鼻插喉強灌水半日增重　牛隻受苦痛極流淚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bNMyiT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bNMyiT</a><br />\n<br />\n幾時先到支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01464625433b050f026523c9494484b7a4b7984","tid":922172,"uid":19725,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:12:58.000Z","msg":"就算食狗肉 都唔應該令動物suffer <br />\n無痛屠宰最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e246fc2095db4cd3a99a71b29d62d9ccdc3461","tid":922172,"uid":9726,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80a1c8cd84b3495b03836e357ca01c81c738871d","tid":922172,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f411275b5ec0a3c2e72ce3a37026f1aa2732e3b4","tid":922172,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181130/_2018113011324714620.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181130%2F_2018113011324714620.jpg&h=1629a0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上周五（23日）內地有傳媒揭發河南偃師高龍鎮207國道邊的小樹林裏，有20多名狗販在給狗灌水。他們用鐵鉗卡頭、水管插胃，狗被灌水時絕望流淚，但還搖著尾巴。狗販稱，買來10元一斤，賣也是10元一斤，給狗灌兩三斤水，能多掙二、三十元，賺的都是給狗灌的水錢。<br />\n<br />\n狗販又表示：「抓著灌灌水，兩隻狗能掙六十多塊錢。有人已經這麼幹了十幾年。」<br />\n<br />\n可見此類殘忍的事件並非首個案例，事件曝光後引發網民極大的憤慨，有網民憤怒地表示：「生而為人 請你們善良！」、「我開始相信有十八層地獄了！」、「前兩天是牛，現在是狗，這些人的良心呢？」、「吃肉是本能，尊重是人性，虐殺動物就為了那麼點錢的顯然沒有人性。」、「看見動物嗷嗷叫的哭求，心裡真的不會痛麼？」、「六十塊錢。有手有腳，幹點甚麼不能掙來六十塊。」、「可以不愛，但請不要傷害！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/876865\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F876865&d=XJlrGENh4tChnQbLgu56%2FU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=835d340a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F876865&h=f6bff575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/876865</a><br />\n<br />\n上一單<br />\n[強國日常] 鼻插喉強灌水半日增重　牛隻受苦痛極流淚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bNMyiT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bNMyiT</a><br />\n<br />\n幾時先到支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:40:03.000Z","msg":"豬一直都受虐待，豬瘟就係大自然既反搏"},{"pid":"944bba263fb6fb86a856438feb2ada76978